    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I've made a workaround by storing a pointer to the configure widget and then remove it manually with removeWidget.  \r\nI've also noticed another related bug:   transformItems from clearRefinements is called multiple times when searching.  Which makes no sense, as the clearRefinment related routines should only be triggered when initiated by the user?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
